{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_01",
  "title": "姉妹の\n限定ユニット",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、……ここで、ターン……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2… Here‚ a turn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "endTime": 7.1333333332999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、やっと、出来た……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa‚ I finally did it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2333333333,
      "endTime": 14.933333333299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、今のところ、すっごく良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan‚ it was really great so far…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "endTime": 19.3278457801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　ありがとう、えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really? Thank you‚ hehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "endTime": 24.1487983067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと休憩しよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we take a little break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "endTime": 26.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……ちょうどいいかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be a good idea…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "endTime": 29.766666666699997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "最近の雫ちゃん……なんだか凄い気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ Shizuku-chan… You seem really amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9333333333,
      "endTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8666666667,
      "endTime": 36.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。この間、瑠依さんとユニットを組んだでしょ？\nあの時から、おっきく見えるっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You formed a team with Rui-san‚ right?\nSince that‚ you've seemed bigger…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "endTime": 45.3875512442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと……？　でも……自信は、結構……ついたと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…? But… I think I gained quite a bit of confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6,
      "endTime": 51.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "だからなのかな？　歌も、ダンスのキレも\n少し前までと全然違うっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that the reason? Both your singing and dancing\nhave changed completely from a little while ago…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8666666667,
      "endTime": 61.0119061491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、千紗ちゃんも、凄い……\n私も、負けられない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Chisa-chan‚ you're amazing too…\nI can't lose either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1666666667,
      "endTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……頑張ろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… Let's do our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "endTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.9999999999945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さんから電話……\nちょっとごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ a call from {user}-san…\nSorry for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "endTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1252.8631198999988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "（雫ちゃんは、凄いって言ってくれたけど……）\n（正直、今の雫ちゃんは……私より、ずっと凄い）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Shizuku-chan said I'm amazing‚ but…)\n(Honestly‚ Shizuku-chan right now… She's way more amazing than me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666666667,
      "endTime": 86.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "（自信がつくとあんなに変わるんだ……嬉しいけど）\n（遠くに行っちゃったみたいで、ちょっと寂しいな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Confidence really changes a person… I'm happy‚ but…)\n(It feels like she's gone far away… It's a little lonely…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1666666667,
      "endTime": 97.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "（私も、もっと頑張りたいけど……）\n（どうしたらいいんだろ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want to work harder too…)\n(I wonder what I should do…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7666666667,
      "endTime": 104.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8033.333333299993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6,
      "endTime": 108.37024941439999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね\n最近、ちょっと悩んでるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…\nLately‚ I've been a little worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666666667,
      "endTime": 114.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな真剣に悩むってことは……\nもしかして、恋！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ if you're seriously worried…\nCould it be… love?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6,
      "endTime": 120.9643589546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います、違います！\n私にはまだその感覚が分かりませんし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ that's not it‚ that's not it!\nI still don't understand that feeling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3,
      "endTime": 127.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　でも、この間のミュージカル凄く良かったよ？\n恋する淑女の語りがもう、最っ高だったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? But that musical you did the other day was really great!\nThe monologue of the lovestruck lady was just amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7333333333,
      "endTime": 137.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。でも、そういう渚ちゃんだって\nこの間の小悪魔なグラビア、とても可愛かったですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But even you‚ Nagisa-chan‚\nThat mischievous gravure you did the other day was really cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4666666667,
      "endTime": 146.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、ありがと。私も手応えあったから\nそう言ってくれると嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ thanks. I had a good feeling about it too.\nI'm glad you say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5666666667,
      "endTime": 152.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……って、沙季ちゃんの悩みを聞こうとしてたんだっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ right. I was trying to ask about your worries‚ Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3666666667,
      "endTime": 157.3000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ふふ、そうでした\n楽しいとつい脱線してしまいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Haha‚ that's right.\nI tend to off the topic when it's interesting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.5666666667,
      "endTime": 164.13333333330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
